Filmed in the Cotswolds and the iconic @abbeyroadstudios, soundtracked by @castbandofficial frontman John Power, the film takes us on a journey about the importance of living your own truth. 

#adidasSPEZIAL returns with a collection of classic footwear silhouettes and carefully considered apparel pieces borrowing references from the 1970s through to the early 90’s.

Arriving July 22nd.
